    "title": "scriptpubkeyman fuzz target TopUp is slow (2/N)",
    "body": "Follow-up to https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/30476\r\n\r\nFound by OSS-Fuzz / https://bugs.chromium.org/p/oss-fuzz/issues/detail?id=70780 \r\n\r\nSeems wasteful to spend time in `TopUp` while fuzzing, so my recommendation would be to limit TopUp iterations a bit.\r\n\r\nContext: [clusterfuzz-testcase-scriptpubkeyman-5934021442338816.bin.txt](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/16409466/clusterfuzz-testcase-scriptpubkeyman-5934021442338816.bin.txt)\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ FUZZ=scriptpubkeyman perf record -g --call-graph dwarf  ./src/test/fuzz/fuzz -runs=1 ./clusterfuzz-testcase-scriptpubkeyman-5934021442338816.bin.txt\r\n$ hotspot  ./perf.data \r\n```\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2024-07-29 10-05-27](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9ad1e830-c24d-436a-8772-cb6c8fccf892)\r\n",
